Child dreams become true
The kindergartens and children's day places in the Zollernalbkreis get post office in these days.
The black forests messenger would like to support the facilities in co-operation with Bauhaus and the savings bank Zollernalb with the realization of their building and adornment desires.
Does the kindergarten need a new sand box?
Join with the action can all kindergartens, children's day places and creches from the entire Zollernalbkreis.
If you have a building or an adornment desire for your facility, you can apply with this with black forests the messenger.
You are creative with your children and surprise you the jury of the action kindergarten building site.
A jury, consisting of representatives of black forests messenger, Bauhaus and Sparkasse Zollernalb, selects three desires from all entries.
Which conditions for the participation are there?
The desire should have to be realized with building material in the value of maximally 2000 euros and on (action) a day.
Beyond that the winner must provide for many industrious building aides.
What has it with the action day and the aides on itself?
Bauhaus makes the material available with support of the savings bank Zollernalb.
It is supplied on the agreed upon day to the kindergarten and is to be processed then directly by the aides.
Aides can be natural parents, grandparents, friends, clubs and the educators and children themselves.
